Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did ask me to make you a Puella Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't ask about the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier if you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami never even found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You humans aren't even aware of your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They exist in your neurons, in your beating hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your body dies, your spirit is annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took out your souls and gave them a form
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they'd be easier to keep safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, fighting Witches would be a bit safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, without telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive to fight like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you got a spear stuck right through your torso,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how much do you think it would hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is true pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were hit just once, you won't even be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to fight Kyoko as long as you did
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you were shielded from that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do that because your body and soul are separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only reason you survived that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go further, you won't feel pain at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then your movements will be slower, so I don't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why does it have to be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you agreed to fight in exchange for your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I did make that wish come true, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show respect!{I do not know what to do with this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura, you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried before. No one believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Kyubey do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't believe he's being cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human values don't mean anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simply payment for the miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is how he'll reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned Sayaka into that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just wanted to heal the man she loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle is still a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made the impossible come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Sayaka Miki had spent her life caring for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would never have been able to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a whole life doesn't normally buy a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's exactly what he's selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean she can never have a normal life back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to give up on Sayaka Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Sayaka hadn't become a Puella Magi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi and I would have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't confuse gratitude with responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way you can save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't owe her anything. You don't have to pay her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get into matters that don't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura, how can you always be so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm no longer human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I face Kyosuke like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moping around, you dunderhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out for a bit. We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you regret it now, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being transformed into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed this kind of power to do the things I've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just paying for what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I'm paying fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just living for yourself, it's all up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hard feelings. No regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think like that, everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste food...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be my dad's church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was kind and honest, to a fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was the type who cried when he read the morning newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He believed you needed a new creed to reach a new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He began preaching things different from the main church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, everyone left his church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main body excommunicated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one wanted to hear what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No surprise there. He looked like some kind of cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to preach the right things, common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one would listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have enough to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand. He wasn't saying anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd listen for just five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd all realize he was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stand it. I couldn't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't watch people refuse to listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I asked Kyubey to make people try to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning, his church was full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More people came to follow him by the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went public as a Puella Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many people followed him, they couldn't fight against the Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I took that as my job, like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my dad and I were saving the world, on the stage and behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, Dad found out my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That all those people had come by magic, not because they believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He scolded me and called me a witch that manipulated peoples' minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a joke? I was the one fighting real Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad broke down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the worst thing for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got drunk, went mad, and killed the entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wish destroyed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished without understanding people, and it made everyone suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never to use my magic for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power was only for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles aren't free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wish for hope, it creates an equivalent despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness evens out and the world stays in balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live paying for what you bring on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be thinking just about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting with the same mistake I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't live with regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already paid more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try and get back some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've learned from my mistake, but you're still making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I misunderstood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for that. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't regret making a wish to help someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I regret that, those feelings will become fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I paid too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use this power to do good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where did you get those apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't appreciate you giving it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! We're Puella Magi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else can understand us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight the way I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get in your way, you can try to kill me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hard feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't feel well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Today, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kamijo's out of the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feeling better, Kamijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to get better staying at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be off my crutches next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great for Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get over there, Sayaka. You haven't talked to him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:17:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been keeping a secret from you and Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, I've been in love with Kyosuke Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that from you. He's quite a catch, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've known Kyosuke for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess... I mean, it's not really a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to be honest with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you face your real feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a precious friend to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of stealing anything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stare at Kamijo even more than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve to try before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow after school, I'll confess to Kamijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you have absolutely no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to tell him how you feel or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why are you so nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just started having regrets today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe if I hadn't saved Hitomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a failure as a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face Mami now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi is going to take Kyosuke away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing I can do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm already dead! A zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hug him with this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't kiss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now. I needed to get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go beat up a Witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fighting a Witch tonight, not a Familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Grief Seed should drop. It's not a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're giving her your prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! She's going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god, I can't watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back. I'll show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away. I can handle this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.46,0:22:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on. Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! If I do it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.16,0:23:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be a different kind of Puella Magi from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.97,0:25:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.92,0:25:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.54,0:25:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use magic just for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a fool.
